name: All-Terrain Armed Scout (AT-AS)
description:
An All-Terrain Armed Scout (AT-AS) is a lightweight, bipedal moving apparatus. It is used for reconnaissance ground operations on difficult terrain.

This is the 1st piece of a new series of moody digital mixed media artworks. The base is an iPhone SE (1 Gen) photography (ProCamera app) and a 3D Blender render of marching cubes export from MagicaVoxel. Retouch and post-processing made in Photoshop, SnapSeed and Procreate.
Resolution: 3946 x 2960 pxl, 264 dpi
